title: Sports Illustrated Model Shows Love For The Green Bay Packers On Instagram
text:
Hailey Clauson (Photo credit: Splash News) 5429894 
Sports Illustrated Swimsuit model Hailey Clauson recently showed her love for the Green Bay Packers on Instagram. A photo posted by Hailey Clauson (@haileyclauson) on Jan 15, 2017 at 1:31pm PST 
Her Instagram is full of other great pictures that are a clear indicator of why she is famous around the world. Click an image below for larger version.
